{"id":67,"parent_id":48,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":67,"title":"Luke 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Luke","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus came to save souls—He gives the parable of the pounds—He rides in triumph into Jerusalem, weeps over the city, and cleanses the temple again."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.1","order":"03.05.019.8138"},["b","1"],"And",["i","Jesus"],"entered and passed through Jericho."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.2","order":"03.05.019.8139"},["b","2"],"And, behold,",["i","there was"],"a man named Zacchæus, which was the chief among the publicans, and he was rich."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.3","order":"03.05.019.8140"},["b","3"],"And he sought to see Jesus who he was; and could not for the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"press"],", because he was little of stature."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.4","order":"03.05.019.8141"},["b","4"],"And he ran before, and climbed up into a sycomore tree to see him: for he was to pass that",["i","way."]],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.5","order":"03.05.019.8142"},["b","5"],"And when Jesus came to the place, he looked up, and saw him, and said unto him, Zacchæus, make haste, and come down; for to day I must abide at thy house."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.6","order":"03.05.019.8143"},["b","6"],"And he made haste, and came down, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"received"],"him joyfully."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.7","order":"03.05.019.8144"},["b","7"],"And when they saw",["i","it,"],"they all murmured, saying, That he was gone to be guest with a man that is a sinner."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.8","order":"03.05.019.8145"},["b","8"],"And Zacchæus stood, and said unto the Lord; Behold, Lord, the half of my goods I give to the poor; and if I have taken any thing from any man by false accusation, I restore",["i","him"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"fourfold"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.9","order":"03.05.019.8146"},["b","9"],"And Jesus said unto him, This day is salvation come to this house, forsomuch as he also is a son of Abraham."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.10","order":"03.05.019.8147"},["b","10"],"For the Son of man is come to seek and to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"save"],"that which was",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"lost"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.11","order":"03.05.019.8148"},["b","11"],"And as they heard these things, he added and spake a parable, because he was nigh to Jerusalem, and because they thought that the kingdom of God should",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"immediately"],"appear."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.12","order":"03.05.019.8149"},["b","12"],"He said therefore, A certain nobleman went into a far country to receive for himself a kingdom, and to return."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.13","order":"03.05.019.8150"},["b","13"],"And he called his ten servants, and delivered them ten",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"pounds"],", and said unto them,",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"Occupy"],"till I come."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.14","order":"03.05.019.8151"},["b","14"],"But his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"citizens"],"hated him, and sent a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"message"],"after him, saying, We will not have this",["i","man"],"to reign over us."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.15","order":"03.05.019.8152"},["b","15"],"And it came to pass, that when he was returned, having received the kingdom, then he commanded these",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"servants"],"to be called unto him, to whom he had given the money, that he might know how much every man had gained by trading."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.16","order":"03.05.019.8153"},["b","16"],"Then came the first, saying, Lord, thy pound hath gained ten pounds."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.17","order":"03.05.019.8154"},["b","17"],"And he said unto him, Well, thou good servant: because thou hast been",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"faithful"],"in a very little, have thou",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"authority"],"over ten cities."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.18","order":"03.05.019.8155"},["b","18"],"And the second came, saying, Lord, thy pound hath gained five pounds."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.19","order":"03.05.019.8156"},["b","19"],"And he said likewise to him, Be thou also over five cities."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.20","order":"03.05.019.8157"},["b","20"],"And another came, saying, Lord, behold,",["i","here is"],"thy pound, which I have kept laid up in a napkin:"],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.21","order":"03.05.019.8158"},["b","21"],"For I",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"feared"],"thee, because thou art an",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"austere"],"man: thou takest up that thou layedst not down, and reapest that thou didst not sow."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.22","order":"03.05.019.8159"},["b","22"],"And he saith unto him, Out of thine own mouth will I judge thee,",["i","thou"],"wicked servant. Thou knewest that I was an austere man, taking up that I laid not down, and reaping that I did not sow:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.23","order":"03.05.019.8160"},["b","23"],"Wherefore then gavest not thou my money into the bank, that at my coming I might have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"required"],"mine own with",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"usury"],"?"],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.24","order":"03.05.019.8161"},["b","24"],"And he said unto them that stood by, Take from him the pound, and give",["i","it"],"to him that hath ten pounds."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.25","order":"03.05.019.8162"},["b","25"],"(And they said unto him, Lord, he hath ten pounds.)"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.26","order":"03.05.019.8163"},["b","26"],"For I say unto you, That unto every one",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"which"],"hath shall be given; and from him that hath not, even that he hath shall be taken away from him."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.27","order":"03.05.019.8164"},["b","27"],"But those mine enemies, which would not that I should reign over them, bring hither, and slay",["i","them"],"before me."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.28","order":"03.05.019.8165"},["b","28"],"¶And when he had thus spoken, he went before, ascending up to Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.29","order":"03.05.019.8166"},["b","29"],"And it came to pass, when he was come nigh to Bethphage and Bethany, at the mount called",["i","the mount"],"of Olives, he sent two of his disciples,"],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.30","order":"03.05.019.8167"},["b","30"],"Saying, Go ye into the village over against",["i","you;"],"in the which at your entering ye shall find a colt tied, whereon yet never man sat: loose him, and bring",["i","him hither."]],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.31","order":"03.05.019.8168"},["b","31"],"And if any man ask you, Why do ye loose",["i","him?"],"thus shall ye say unto him, Because the Lord hath need of him."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.32","order":"03.05.019.8169"},["b","32"],"And they that were sent went their way, and found even as he had said unto them."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.33","order":"03.05.019.8170"},["b","33"],"And as they were loosing the colt, the owners thereof said unto them, Why loose ye the colt?"],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.34","order":"03.05.019.8171"},["b","34"],"And they said, The Lord hath need of him."],["div",{"id":"35","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.35","order":"03.05.019.8172"},["b","35"],"And they brought him to Jesus: and they cast their garments upon the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_35a"},"colt"],", and they set Jesus thereon."],["div",{"id":"36","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.36","order":"03.05.019.8173"},["b","36"],"And as he went, they spread their clothes in the way."],["div",{"id":"37","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.37","order":"03.05.019.8174"},["b","37"],"And when he was come nigh, even now at the descent of the mount of Olives, the whole multitude of the disciples began to rejoice and praise God with a loud voice for all the mighty works that they had seen;"],["div",{"id":"38","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.38","order":"03.05.019.8175"},["b","38"],"Saying, Blessed",["i","be"],"the King that cometh in the name of the Lord: peace in heaven, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_38a"},"glory"],"in the highest."],["div",{"id":"39","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.39","order":"03.05.019.8176"},["b","39"],"And some of the Pharisees from among the multitude said unto him, Master, rebuke thy disciples."],["div",{"id":"40","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.40","order":"03.05.019.8177"},["b","40"],"And he answered and said unto them, I tell you that, if these should hold their peace, the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_40a"},"stones"],"would immediately cry out."],["div",{"id":"41","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.41","order":"03.05.019.8178"},["b","41"],"¶And when he was come near, he beheld the city, and wept over it,"],["div",{"id":"42","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.42","order":"03.05.019.8179"},["b","42"],"Saying, If thou hadst known, even thou, at least in this thy day, the things",["i","which belong"],"unto thy peace! but now they are hid from thine eyes."],["div",{"id":"43","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.43","order":"03.05.019.8180"},["b","43"],"For the days shall come upon thee, that thine",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_43a"},"enemies"],"shall cast a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_43b"},"trench"],"about thee, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_43c"},"compass"],"thee round, and keep thee in on every side,"],["div",{"id":"44","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.44","order":"03.05.019.8181"},["b","44"],"And shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_44a"},"lay"],"thee even with the ground, and thy children within thee; and they shall not leave in thee one",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_44b"},"stone"],"upon another; because thou knewest not the time of thy",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_44c"},"visitation"],"."],["div",{"id":"45","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.45","order":"03.05.019.8182"},["b","45"],"And he went into the temple, and began to cast out them that sold therein, and them that bought;"],["div",{"id":"46","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.46","order":"03.05.019.8183"},["b","46"],"Saying unto them, It is written, My house is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_46a"},"house"],"of prayer: but ye have made it a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_46b"},"den"],"of thieves."],["div",{"id":"47","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.47","order":"03.05.019.8184"},["b","47"],"And he taught daily in the temple. But the chief priests and the scribes and the chief of the people sought to destroy him,"],["div",{"id":"48","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.48","order":"03.05.019.8185"},["b","48"],"And could not find what they might do: for all the people were very attentive to hear him."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.3a","order":"03.05.019.8186"},["b","3a"],["span.small","GR"],"crowd, multitude."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.6a","order":"03.05.019.8188"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hospitality"},"TG Hospitality"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.8a","order":"03.05.019.8190"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-sam/12.6"},"2 Sam. 12:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.10a","order":"03.05.019.8192"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/life-sanctity-of"},"TG Life, Sanctity of"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.10b","order":"03.05.019.8194"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.16"},"Ezek. 34:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/26.25.23-29"},"2 Ne. 26:25 (23–29)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.11a","order":"03.05.019.8196"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-thes/2.2.1-6"},"2 Thes. 2:2 (1–6)"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.13a","order":"03.05.019.8198"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/talents"},"TG Talents"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.13b","order":"03.05.019.8200"},["b","13b"],["span.small","GR"],"Do business."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.14a","order":"03.05.019.8202"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.14b","order":"03.05.019.8204"},["b","14b"],["span.small","GR"],"ambassador."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.15a","order":"03.05.019.8206"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/72.3.3-4"},"D&C 72:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.17a","order":"03.05.019.8208"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/stewardship"},"TG Stewardship"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.17b","order":"03.05.019.8210"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/authority"},"TG Authority"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.21a","order":"03.05.019.8212"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courage"},"TG Courage"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fearful"},"Fearful"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.21b","order":"03.05.019.8214"},["b","21b"],["span.small","GR"],"harsh, ungenerous."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.23a","order":"03.05.019.8216"},["b","23a"],["span.small","GR"],"collected."],["div",{"id":"23b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.23b","order":"03.05.019.8218"},["b","23b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/usury"},"TG Usury"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.26a","order":"03.05.019.8220"},["b","26a"],["span.small","JST"],"Luke 19:25 …",["i","who occupieth,"],"shall be given; and from him",["i","who occupieth"],"not, even that he hath",["i","received"],"shall be taken away from him."],["div",{"id":"35a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.35a","order":"03.05.019.8222"},["b","35a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/9.9"},"Zech. 9:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"38a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.38a","order":"03.05.019.8224"},["b","38a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/2.14"},"Luke 2:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"40a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.40a","order":"03.05.019.8226"},["b","40a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/21.9"},"Matt. 21:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"43a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.43a","order":"03.05.019.8228"},["b","43a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/21.20"},"Luke 21:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"43b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.43b","order":"03.05.019.8230"},["b","43b"],["span.small","GR"],"fortification, rampart.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/37.33"},"Isa. 37:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"43c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.43c","order":"03.05.019.8232"},["b","43c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.52"},"Deut. 28:52"],"."],["div",{"id":"44a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.44a","order":"03.05.019.8234"},["b","44a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/9.26"},"Dan. 9:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"44b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.44b","order":"03.05.019.8236"},["b","44b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.2.1-51"},"Matt. 24:2 (1–51)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-m/1.3.1-55"},"JS—M 1:3 (1–55)"],"."],["div",{"id":"44c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.44c","order":"03.05.019.8238"},["b","44c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.3"},"Isa. 10:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"46a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.46a","order":"03.05.019.8240"},["b","46a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/56.7"},"Isa. 56:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"46b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.46b","order":"03.05.019.8242"},["b","46b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.11"},"Jer. 7:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/94.8.8-9"},"D&C 94:8 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/109.20.19-20"},"109:20 (19–20)"],"."]]}
